s to Seattle Seahawks |work=Detroit Lions |date=October 22, 2019 |accessdate=October 22, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Staff==\n{{Detroit Lions staff}}\n\n==Current roster==\n{{Detroit Lions roster}}\n\n==Preseason==\nThe Lions' preseason opponents and schedule will be announced in the spring.\n==Regular season==\n<!--===Schedule===-->\n===2020 opponents===\nListed below are the Lions' opponents for [[2020 NFL season|2020]]. Exact dates and times will be announced on May 9, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=2020 Opponents Determined |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/2020-Opponents-Determined.aspx |work=NFL Communications |date=December 30, 2019 |accessdate=December 30, 2019}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2020|border=2}}\"| Category !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Home !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Away\n|-\n| '''Division opponents'''<br>([[NFC North]]) || colspan=2| [[2020 Chicago Bears season|Chicago Bears]]<br>[[2020 Green Bay Packers season|Green Bay Packers]]<br>[[2020 Minnesota Vikings season|Minnesota Vikings]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>([[NFC South]]) || [[2020 New Orleans Saints season|New Orleans Saints]]<br>[[2020 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]] || [[2020 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta Falcons]]<br>[[2020 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>(based on {{nfly|2019}} division placement) || [[2020 Washington Redskins season|Washington Redskins]] || [[2020 Arizona Cardinals season|Arizona Cardinals]]\n|-\n| '''Interconference opponents'''<br>([[AFC South]]) || [[2020 Houston Texans season|Houston Texans]]<br>[[2020 Indianapolis Colts season|Indianapolis Colts]] || [[2020 Jacksonville Jaguars season|Jacksonville Jaguars]]<br>[[2020 Tennessee Titans season|Tennessee Titans]]\n|}\n<!--\n===Game summaries===\n====Week #: vs. Ch